Holy Sacrifice
Discworld ritual help
Holy Sacrifice

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Holy Sacrifice - Lends mental power through physical sacrifice.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Holy sacrifice allows the priest to convert their physical endurance
to mental strength, by offering their blood and hit points to their
god in exchange for guild points.  The effectiveness of the transfer
is influenced by your skill in performing miscellaneous rituals.
You will require a dagger and a holy symbol to perform this ritual.
.EP
